As pastas com o código encontram-se dentro da pasta "Source code".

-> Programa em C#:
Na pasta "C#", executar no terminal:

sudo apt update
sudo apt install mono-complete
mcs -out:csbin.exe Matrix.cs
mono csbin.exe

-> Programa em C/C++:
Na pasta "cpp", executar no terminal (para ver informação "usage" executar apenas ./bincpp):

g++ -I/usr/local/include -O0 main.cpp /usr/local/lib/libpapi.a -o bincpp -fopenmp -O3
./bincpp <operation> <size> <num_of_threads>

-> Programa em Java:
Na pasta "java", executar no terminal:

javac Main.java
java Main <operation> <size>
operation: 1, 2 or 3
size: matrix size

operation 1 : performance of multiplication of NxN matrices (naive algorithm)
operation 2 : performance of multiplication of NxN matrices (optimized algorithm)
operation 3 : ratio betwen the two algorithms

-> Programa em Python:
Na pasta "python", executar no terminal:

python "Source.py" <size>
size: matrix size
